  "dialogue": [
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "So, when did you live in Morocco?",
      "zh": "那麼，你什麼時候住在摩洛哥？",
      "ja": "それで、いつモロッコに住んでいたの？",
      "time": "00:00:00"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Oh, in the late 90s.",
      "zh": "哦，九十年代末。",
      "ja": "ああ、90年代後半だよ。",
      "time": "00:00:06"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "I kind of bounced around to a bunch of different places over the past few years.",
      "zh": "過去幾年我大概去了很多不同的地方。",
      "ja": "ここ数年、いろんな場所を転々としていたんだ。",
      "time": "00:00:07"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Oh, yeah? Like where?",
      "zh": "哦，是嗎？像哪些地方？",
      "ja": "そうなの？どんなところ？",
      "time": "00:00:10"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Oh, God, where? Let's see. Austin is Dumbo, Sri Lanka, Portland, Costa Rica, Buffalo.",
      "zh": "哦，天啊，哪裡呢？讓我想想。奧斯汀、Dumbo、斯里蘭卡、波特蘭、哥斯大黎加、布法羅。",
      "ja": "ああ、どこだっけ？えっと、オースティン、ダンボ、スリランカ、ポートランド、コスタリカ、バッファロー。",
      "time": "00:00:11"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "A couple other places.",
      "zh": "還有其他幾個地方。",
      "ja": "他にもいくつかあるよ。",
      "time": "00:00:18"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Wow, were you in the Peace Corps?",
      "zh": "哇，你是和平隊成員嗎？",
      "ja": "わあ、ピースコーにいたの？",
      "time": "00:00:19"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "No, I just like to move a lot.",
      "zh": "不，我只是喜歡經常搬家。",
      "ja": "いや、ただよく動き回るのが好きなだけ。",
      "time": "00:00:20"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "You know, I kind of get stir-crazy if I'm stuck in one place for too long.",
      "zh": "你知道的，如果我被困在一個地方太久，我會感到很煩躁。",
      "ja": "わかるでしょ、同じ場所に長くいるとイライラしてくるんだ。",
      "time": "00:00:22"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "You know what I mean?",
      "zh": "你懂我的意思吧？",
      "ja": "わかるでしょ？",
      "time": "00:00:24"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Oh, yeah, completely.",
      "zh": "哦，完全懂。",
      "ja": "ああ、完全にわかるよ。",
      "time": "00:00:25"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "No, remember you were the person who-",
      "zh": "不，記得你是那個人-",
      "ja": "いや、君はあの人だったよね-",
      "time": "00:00:26"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Oh, my God, I can't believe.",
      "zh": "哦，天啊，我不敢相信。",
      "ja": "ああ、信じられない。",
      "time": "00:00:29"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Oh, of course, you were like the greatest delegate model you in history.",
      "zh": "哦，當然，你是史上最棒的代表模範。",
      "ja": "ああ、もちろん、君は史上最高の代表モデルだったよね。",
      "time": "00:00:32"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "I guess I did manage to pass a few resolutions.",
      "zh": "我想我確實通過了幾項決議。",
      "ja": "いくつか決議案を通せたと思うよ。",
      "time": "00:00:36"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Are you okay?",
      "zh": "你還好嗎？",
      "ja": "大丈夫？",
      "time": "00:00:40"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Because you're sweating pretty profusely.",
      "zh": "因為你流了很多汗。",
      "ja": "すごく汗かいてるよ。",
      "time": "00:00:42"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Yeah, no, I'm fine.",
      "zh": "是的，不，我沒事。",
      "ja": "うん、大丈夫だよ。",
      "time": "00:00:44"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "I always react this way to spicy food.",
      "zh": "我吃辣的食物總是這樣反應。",
      "ja": "辛い食べ物にはいつもこうなるんだ。",
      "time": "00:00:45"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Okay.",
      "zh": "好。",
      "ja": "わかった。",
      "time": "00:00:47"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Yeah, but I love it.",
      "zh": "是的，但我很喜歡。",
      "ja": "うん、でも大好きだよ。",
      "time": "00:00:48"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "God, you know, I can't believe you're not married.",
      "zh": "天啊，你知道嗎，我不敢相信你還沒結婚。",
      "ja": "まったく、君が結婚してないなんて信じられないよ。",
      "time": "00:00:49"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I mean, even when we were kids,",
      "zh": "我是說，即使我們還是小孩時，",
      "ja": "子供の頃から、",
      "time": "00:00:51"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I always saw you as that guy that would settle down at a young age.",
      "zh": "我總覺得你會早早安定下來。",
      "ja": "君は若いうちに落ち着く人だと思ってた。",
      "time": "00:00:52"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "You know, you were always kind of like an old young guy.",
      "zh": "你知道的，你總是有點像個老成的年輕人。",
      "ja": "君はいつもどこか大人びた若者だったよね。",
      "time": "00:00:55"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Yeah, well, it just hasn't happened.",
      "zh": "是啊，只是還沒發生而已。",
      "ja": "うん、でもまだそうなってないんだ。",
      "time": "00:00:57"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "But what about you?",
      "zh": "但你呢？",
      "ja": "でも君はどう？",
      "time": "00:01:00"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Hmm?",
      "zh": "嗯？",
      "ja": "ん？",
      "time": "00:01:01"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "You ever gotten closer?",
      "zh": "你有沒有更接近那個目標？",
      "ja": "結婚に近づいたことある？",
      "time": "00:01:02"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Oh, to the whole marriage thing?",
      "zh": "哦，指的是結婚這件事？",
      "ja": "ああ、結婚のこと？",
      "time": "00:01:03"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Oh, God, no, no way.",
      "zh": "哦，天啊，不，絕不可能。",
      "ja": "ああ、絶対にないよ。",
      "time": "00:01:04"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "No, no, no, no, no, no, no, no, no, no, no, no, no.",
      "zh": "不，不，不，不，不，不，不，不，不，不，不，不，不。",
      "ja": "いやいやいやいやいやいやいやいやいやいやいやいや。",
      "time": "00:01:05"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "I'm not really big on the whole long-term commitment thing.",
      "zh": "我不太喜歡長期承諾這種事。",
      "ja": "長期的な約束事はあまり好きじゃないんだ。",
      "time": "00:01:08"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Why are you coming out of a bad relationship or...?",
      "zh": "你是剛結束一段糟糕的關係嗎？",
      "ja": "悪い関係から抜け出したばかり？",
      "time": "00:01:11"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "No, I'm kind of coming out of like eight bad relationships.",
      "zh": "不，我大概是結束了八段糟糕的感情。",
      "ja": "いや、8回くらい悪い関係を終えたところだよ。",
      "time": "00:01:14"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "You sure I can't get you to tell or something.",
      "zh": "你確定我不能讓你說說嗎？",
      "ja": "話してくれない？",
      "time": "00:01:17"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "No, no, no, no, good, but I mean, if the right person came along, things might be different, right?",
      "zh": "不，不，不，不，沒事，但我是說，如果遇到對的人，情況可能會不同，對吧？",
      "ja": "いやいや、大丈夫。でも、もし運命の人が現れたら変わるかもね。",
      "time": "00:01:20"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Oh, yeah.",
      "zh": "哦，是啊。",
      "ja": "ああ、そうだね。",
      "time": "00:01:24"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "You're probably right.",
      "zh": "你說得對。",
      "ja": "たぶんその通りだね。",
      "time": "00:01:26"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Sorry.",
      "zh": "抱歉。",
      "ja": "ごめん。",
      "time": "00:01:28"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Hey, you might have to go to the men's room.",
      "zh": "嘿，你可能得去男廁。",
      "ja": "ねえ、男子トイレに行かなきゃかも。",
      "time": "00:01:30"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Please.",
      "zh": "拜託。",
      "ja": "お願い。",
      "time": "00:01:33"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Sure.",
      "zh": "當然。",
      "ja": "いいよ。",
      "time": "00:01:35"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Oh, my.",
      "zh": "哦，我的天。",
      "ja": "あらまあ。",
      "time": "00:01:36"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Occupied.",
      "zh": "有人了。",
      "ja": "使用中。",
      "time": "00:01:37"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "I'm going to be here all night, dude.",
      "zh": "我今晚都會在這裡，老兄。",
      "ja": "今夜ずっとここにいるよ、兄弟。",
      "time": "00:01:39"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "All right.",
      "zh": "好吧。",
      "ja": "わかった。",
      "time": "00:01:43"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Well, this is me.",
      "zh": "嗯，這是我。",
      "ja": "さて、これが僕だ。",
      "time": "00:01:46"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "All right.",
      "zh": "好吧。",
      "ja": "よし。",
      "time": "00:01:48"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Watch more stairs in a magazine coffee or tea.",
      "zh": "看更多樓梯，喝杯咖啡或茶。",
      "ja": "雑誌を見ながらコーヒーかお茶でも。",
      "time": "00:01:49"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "OK.",
      "zh": "好。",
      "ja": "わかった。",
      "time": "00:01:52"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Um, it's got to find my keys here.",
      "zh": "嗯，我得在這裡找我的鑰匙。",
      "ja": "えっと、ここで鍵を探さなきゃ。",
      "time": "00:01:53"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Uh-oh.",
      "zh": "糟了。",
      "ja": "やばい。",
      "time": "00:01:56"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Right there.",
      "zh": "就在那裡。",
      "ja": "あそこだ。",
      "time": "00:02:01"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Oh, yeah.",
      "zh": "哦，是的。",
      "ja": "ああ、そうだ。",
      "time": "00:02:06"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "OK.",
      "zh": "好。",
      "ja": "わかった。",
      "time": "00:02:07"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Oh, wow.",
      "zh": "哦，哇。",
      "ja": "おお、すごい。",
      "time": "00:02:08"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "It's great.",
      "zh": "真棒。",
      "ja": "素晴らしいね。",
      "time": "00:02:09"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "It's so cozy.",
      "zh": "好溫馨。",
      "ja": "とても居心地がいい。",
      "time": "00:02:10"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Nice.",
      "zh": "不錯。",
      "ja": "いいね。",
      "time": "00:02:11"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Did you just move in or?",
      "zh": "你是剛搬進來嗎？",
      "ja": "引っ越したばかり？",
      "time": "00:02:12"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "No.",
      "zh": "不。",
      "ja": "いいえ。",
      "time": "00:02:13"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "And you're about four months?",
      "zh": "你大概住了四個月？",
      "ja": "4ヶ月くらい？",
      "time": "00:02:14"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Uh-huh.",
      "zh": "嗯哼。",
      "ja": "うん。",
      "time": "00:02:15"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Right in the house.",
      "zh": "就在這房子裡。",
      "ja": "この家の中だね。",
      "time": "00:02:16"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Oh, no, no.",
      "zh": "哦，不，不。",
      "ja": "ああ、違うよ。",
      "time": "00:02:17"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "This is Redojo.",
      "zh": "這是Redojo。",
      "ja": "これはレドホだよ。",
      "time": "00:02:18"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "He's a ferret.",
      "zh": "他是一隻雪貂。",
      "ja": "フェレットなんだ。",
      "time": "00:02:19"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "I got him in Sicily at a flea market years ago.",
      "zh": "幾年前我在西西里的一個跳蚤市場買的。",
      "ja": "何年か前にシチリアのフリーマーケットで買ったんだ。",
      "time": "00:02:21"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "He's old.",
      "zh": "他年紀大了。",
      "ja": "もう年寄りだよ。",
      "time": "00:02:23"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "We can't really see anymore.",
      "zh": "他視力不好了。",
      "ja": "もうあまり見えないんだ。",
      "time": "00:02:24"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Cute.",
      "zh": "好可愛。",
      "ja": "かわいいね。",
      "time": "00:02:26"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Hey, you mind if I use your bathroom?",
      "zh": "嘿，我可以用你的浴室嗎？",
      "ja": "ねえ、トイレ使ってもいい？",
      "time": "00:02:27"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Oh, sure.",
      "zh": "哦，當然。",
      "ja": "ああ、いいよ。",
      "time": "00:02:29"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "zh": "是的。",
      "ja": "うん。",
      "time": "00:02:30"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Oh, actually, that's not the bathroom.",
      "zh": "哦，實際上，那不是浴室。",
      "ja": "ああ、実はあれはトイレじゃないんだ。",
      "time": "00:02:31"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Oh, my bathroom's right here.",
      "zh": "哦，我的浴室就在這裡。",
      "ja": "トイレはこっちだよ。",
      "time": "00:02:32"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Oh.",
      "zh": "哦。",
      "ja": "ああ。",
      "time": "00:02:33"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "OK.",
      "zh": "好。",
      "ja": "わかった。",
      "time": "00:02:34"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Yeah, because I just, uh, had a lot to drink, a lot of water.",
      "zh": "是的，因為我剛喝了很多水。",
      "ja": "そう、たくさん飲んだから、水をね。",
      "time": "00:02:35"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "OK.",
      "zh": "好。",
      "ja": "わかった。",
      "time": "00:02:38"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "I'll just be a second.",
      "zh": "我馬上回來。",
      "ja": "すぐ戻るよ。",
      "time": "00:02:39"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "OK, take your time.",
      "zh": "好，慢慢來。",
      "ja": "うん、ゆっくりしてね。",
      "time": "00:02:41"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "I don't believe this.",
      "zh": "我不敢相信這個。",
      "ja": "信じられない。",
      "time": "00:02:48"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Oh, wait.",
      "zh": "哦，等等。",
      "ja": "ああ、待って。",
      "time": "00:02:50"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Oh, wait.",
      "zh": "哦，等等。",
      "ja": "ああ、待って。",
      "time": "00:02:55"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Go away.",
      "zh": "走開。",
      "ja": "どいて。",
      "time": "00:02:57"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Come, come, come, come, come, come, come, come.",
      "zh": "來，來，來，來，來，來，來，來。",
      "ja": "こっち、こっち、こっち、こっち、こっち、こっち、こっち、こっち。",
      "time": "00:02:59"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Ow, ow.",
      "zh": "哎呀，哎呀。",
      "ja": "痛い、痛い。",
      "time": "00:03:01"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Ow.",
      "zh": "哎呀。",
      "ja": "痛い。",
      "time": "00:03:02"
